QUERY_STATE_AM - Static variable in interface com.ihealth.communication.control.AmProfile
The key of state information.
Value:

queryDeviceCloudInfo(String, String, String, String) - Method in class com.ihealth.communication.control.UpgradeControl
Query device cloud upgrade information This is an asynchronous call, it will return immediately. If start successfully, following callback will be triggered:
iHealthDevicesCallback.onDeviceNotify(String mac, String deviceType, String action, String message)
The action will be: ACTION_DEVICE_CLOUD_FIRMWARE_VERSION The keys of the message will show in KeyList of the action. If error happens, following callback will be triggered:
iHealthDevicesCallback.onDeviceNotify(String mac, String deviceType, String action, String message)
The action will be DEVICE_UP_ERROR The message will be a JSON string with error ID,
the keys will show in the KeyList of the action.
queryDeviceFirmwareInfo(String, String) - Method in class com.ihealth.communication.control.UpgradeControl
Query the firmware firmware information This is an asynchronous call, it will return immediately. If start successfully, following callback will be triggered:
iHealthDevicesCallback.onDeviceNotify(String mac, String deviceType, String action, String message)
The action will be: ACTION_DEVICE_UP_INFO The keys of the message will show in KeyList of the action. If error happens, following callback will be triggered:
iHealthDevicesCallback.onDeviceNotify(String mac, String deviceType, String action, String message)
The action will be DEVICE_UP_ERROR The message will be a JSON string with error ID,
the keys will show in the KeyList of the action.
queryUpgradeInfoFromDeviceAndCloud(String, String) - Method in class com.ihealth.communication.manager.iHealthDevicesUpgradeManager
Get version information from device and cloud.
